{"tid":1837741,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"2019年武漢同香港都發生過示威...","createTime":"2020-01-23T18:06:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T07:54:22.000Z","uid":343233,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d817d52d1c88dc3f76b3a21b014e2e04be298ec5","tid":1837741,"uid":343233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T18:06:43.000Z","msg":"2019年7月武漢因為興建焚化爐發生過示威，<br />\n<br />\n同年，香港反共騷動至今都未平息。<br />\n<br />\n回一回帶，2018年1月5日位於武漢嘅P4實驗室正式投入運行。是為首個研究高致病性病源微生物嘅P4實驗室，專門研究最危險、傳染性最強嘅病毒，包括<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">SARS</span></span></strong>、伊波拉。<br />\n<br />\n直至今日，仲有武漢來港嘅航班，新年期間大陸車輛可以免費經港豬澳大橋落嚟，搭高鐵嘅武漢旅客填好健康申報表後就可以入境。<br />\n<br />\n最後想提一提V for Vendetta(V煞)入面執政黨Norsefire迅速平息騷動嘅手段，<span style=\"color: red;\">係透過研發病毒令8萬平民死亡同令其他人恐慌同絕望，再發明疫苗得到人民信任同執政權力</span>，開始咗Norsefire嘅極權統治。<br />\n<br />\n以上純粹將幾件事同一部電影嘅劇情整合，無其他意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n願眾人平安。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n武漢示威<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-48881707\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-48881707&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeFKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=d660d32b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-48881707&h=2c358a6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-48881707</a><br />\n<br />\nP4研究室<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2020-01-23/28312252\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2020-01-23%2F28312252&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeFKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=84c11024\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2020-01-23/28312252</a><br />\n<br />\nV for Vendetta劇情<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/V%E6%80%AA%E5%AE%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2FV%25E6%2580%25AA%25E5%25AE%25A2&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeFKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=03d789d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/V%E6%80%AA%E5%AE%A2</a>"},{"pid":"bb38c0b295058467e352ae068ff7c0a5f9b58a14","tid":1837741,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T18:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4da75cfabd7df81aa0684a1c081d77969c1a2d7","tid":1837741,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T18:08:01.000Z","msg":"入來推十下！<br />\n<br />\n「突發」四個醫療工會不排除於初四後發起工業行動！(終極整合）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837445</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ae479d72c756eafeeaddb80f7ca503b760b08bae","tid":1837741,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T18:08:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c473a5a97c24ab895b47832bd93f74ec46c4e17e","tid":1837741,"uid":310572,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T18:08:45.000Z","msg":"支那撚研究到"},{"pid":"a7ac91a7b2e98e6785d547235d1fb063f251e1bd","tid":1837741,"uid":343233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c473a5a97c24ab895b47832bd93f74ec46c4e17e","tid":1837741,"uid":310572,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T18:08:45.000Z","msg":"支那撚研究到"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T18:13:16.000Z","msg":"研究到個病毒，研究唔到個疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb335eed7c9c1df7cdee42efe90041e4abc92db","tid":1837741,"uid":310572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7ac91a7b2e98e6785d547235d1fb063f251e1bd","tid":1837741,"uid":343233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"s